comments: Washington (CHA) is established in Jokic's (DEN) path and absorbs the marginal contact during the play at the basket.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) legally contests Oubre Jr.'s (CHA) jump shot attempt.
Oubre Jr. (CHA) reaches for the ball and marginal contact occurs with Murray's (DEN) arm as he maintains his dribble on the perimeter.
Brown (DEN) establishes himself in Oubre Jr.'s (CHA) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Oubre Jr. (CHA) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Murray (DEN) during the steal attempt.
Oubre Jr. (CHA) and Murray (DEN) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Gordon (DEN) establishes himself in Washington's (CHA) path and absorbs the marginal contact as they briefly engage during the screen.
Oubre Jr. (CHA) reaches in and initiates contact with Murray's (DEN) wrist, which pulls his hand off the ball and dislodges it.

Ball (CHA) makes clean contact with the ball to dislodge it as Murray (DEN) tries to regain possession off the loose ball. Any follow-through arm contact after the ball is dislodged is deemed incidental.
Brown (DEN) reaches for the ball and marginal contact occurs as he brushes Washington's (CHA) arm at the end of his drive.
Plumlee (CHA) commits a take foul on Gordon (DEN).
Oubre Jr. (CHA) initiates contact with Murray's (DEN) arm, which dislodges the ball out of bounds.
Jokic (DEN) retracts his arm from Ball's (CHA) path and marginal contact occurs during the play at the basket.
Oubre Jr. (CHA) reaches across and makes contact with Murray's (DEN) arm, which affects his ability to control the pass.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) jumps vertically and avoids contact with Ball's (CHA) arms during his contest on the driving shot attempt.
Washington (CHA) commits a take foul on Jokic (DEN) prior to the start of his shooting motion.
Gordon (DEN) reaches for the loose ball and marginal contact occurs with Hayward's (CHA) arm as he secures the rebound.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) rests his hand on Washington's (CHA) side and marginal contact occurs during the dunk at the basket.
Jokic (DEN) makes marginal contact with Hayward (CHA) when releasing from the post engagement during the inbound.
Hayward (CHA) grabs Jokic's (DEN) arm prior to him receiving the pass and a personal foul is correctly assessed.
Plumlee (CHA) establishes himself in Brown's (DEN) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) briefly rests his hand on Hayward's (CHA) body and marginal contact occurs as they engage during the screen.
Plumlee (CHA) establishes himself in Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) path and does not deliver illegal contact.

comments: Washington (CHA) can't control the pass and is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
